title: Ramin Djawadi & Brandon Campbell - 5x10 - Playing By The Rules
author: POISuit
comment: Just want to say that this is a really good rip. It's nearly impossible to get all the dialogue and sound effects out without ruining the track, but you did a really impressive job cleaning them up, to the point where I could almost use this track in another show.
It was in that moment that Samaritan knew. It fucked up.
I thought the "Dark Finch" motif from 5x12 (when he installs the virus) was introduced in that episode, but there it is! 3:59 / 4:55
One of my favorite scenes/tracks from the entire show.
I have played by the rules for so long....
description:
From 5x10 'The Day The World Went Away'
Composed by: Ramin Djawadi & Brandon Campbell
